No matter who you are, if you bring

Known as the Forest Witch, if you are

It sneaks into people’s homes, taking

With sly cunning, it lures people into

Its hairs work like muscle fibers.

It evolved after experiencing numerous

What appears to be an iron helmet is

Be cautious of the ectoplasmic body

After deflecting attacks with its hard

Its amusing movements make it very

Never touch its shadowlike body, or

It evolved from a Milcery that held

The six of them work together as one.

It feeds on seaweed, using its teeth

It eats snow that piles up on the

Icy scales fall from its wings

Once a year, on a specific date and

It drifted in on the flow of ocean

Through its horns, it can pick up on

As it eats the seeds stored up in its

These Pokémon live in herds. Their
trunks have incredible grip strength,

The powerful muscles in its tail

The shaking of its freezing upper half

Its mighty legs are capable of running

The skin on its face is impervious

Its body resembles polished metal,

After being reborn as a ghost, Dreepy

It’s capable of flying faster than 120

Apparently the Dreepy inside its horns

It  has slumbered for many years. Some

It slept for aeons while in the form

It was inside a meteorite that fell

If it pulls the long white hair on

Inhabiting the mountains of a distant

Once the vines on its body tear off,

Its entire body is made of an organ

Its body is composed of crystallized

As it dashes through the night, it

Its every move is filled with grace

The fur shed from its beard retains

Parts of its body turned to stone when

burly physique and newfound capacity to manipulate peat

This Pokémon is cloaked in the souls of its
comrades who perished during a punishing

Because of Sneasler's virulent poison and

Overqwil’s poisonous spikes will reflexively

The sweet scent its body gives off

It lies on warm rocks and uses the

Pawmo uses a unique fighting technique in which it uses its forepaws to strike foes and zap them with electricity from its paw pads simultaneously.

The surface of this Pokémon's skin

This calm Pokémon is very compassionate.

Its firepower increases when it fights,

This Pokémon can store energy in its

This Pokémon lives on sheer cliffs.

It rolls its mud ball around while the energy

It emits psychic power from the gaps

This Pokémon can pick up the scent

A variety of fish Pokémon,
Wugtrio was once considered

It absorbs nutrients from cave walls.

This Pokémon is a glutton,
